skdetail:
Rated: Mature. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: yo mama
des: This skill enables you to say what type of mama joke you want back. The joke categories include: fat, dumb, old, and ugly. More categories will be added weekly. This skill may not be suitable for all ages.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
